<h1>Pacific Land Marine Stage</h1>
<p>The kids were quite excited to start the day with an animal show, featuring monkeys, sea lions, and dolphins. The trainers and animals were all very impressive. Next to Pacific Land, there's a restaurant that has a large outdoor dining area in the back, where you can get some great views overlooking the ocean and surfers.</p>
