<h1>Lunch at Hanseusi, and the beach</h1>
<p>Wife and kids love sushi and Japanese food, so we went to another Japanese spot for lunch. Very typical menu, with donkatsu (fried pork), some raw-fish bibimbap, and some sashimi. Everything was good, and while I prefer the ramen we had last night, this place was not bad. After lunch, we headed over to the same beach (Geumneung Beach) again to let the kids play.</p>
